cs.NI, cs.CY, cs.SE, cs.DC, cs.DS

Reasoning: 
- cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture) is the most likely category as the paper discusses the design and deployment of an IoT infrastructure for environmental monitoring and management. 
- cs.CY (Cryptography and Security) is also a likely category as the paper may discuss security measures implemented in the IoT infrastructure. 
- cs.SE (Software Engineering) is a possible category as the paper may discuss the software design and development of the IoT infrastructure. 
- cs.DC (Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing) is a possible category as the paper may discuss the distributed nature of the IoT infrastructure. 
- cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) is a possible category as the paper may discuss the algorithms used for data processing and analysis in the IoT infrastructure.
